  "uiSignature": "Four gender/number chips (masc, fem, neut, plural) across the top. For я/ты sentences, show a user gender badge or explicit gender selector.",
  "subdeckRules": [
    "Start with endings, then full forms, then sentence conversion.",
    "Do not force the user to guess speaker gender for я/ты; the UI must supply it.",
    "Special verbs быть and есть belong in their own subdeck."
  ],
